    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in great shape for all your daily commutes or weekend adventures. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a charm, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for something dependable and high-quality. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take a look, and see for yourself how great it drives!",
      "price": 32000.0,
