      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically robust, with the high-pressure VANOS system recently serviced for optimal variable valve timing. The chassis has been enhanced with proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in response. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-Variable Differential, ensuring linear torque delivery. While the exterior displays minor road wear consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain and cooling system are in excellent health, free of common heat-cycle fatigue. A mechanically sorted specimen for the enthusiast who prioritizes tactile feedback and engineering integrity.",
